"""
PART III Income

15. Income for the purposes of the Act

(1)

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

For the purposes of section 15(1)(e) (income), all social security benefits are prescribed except—

(d)

a payment under regulations made in exercise of the power conferred by paragraph 7(2)(b) of Part II of Schedule 8 to the 1992 Act;
"""

relevant_payment_is_social_security_benefit:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

relevant_payment_is_under_regulations_made_in_exercise_of_the_power_conferred_by_paragraph_7_2_b_of_part_ii_of_schedule_8_to_the_1992_act:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

relevant_payment_falls_within_exception_to_prescribed_social_security_benefits_for_income_15_1_d:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        relevant_payment_is_social_security_benefit and relevant_payment_is_under_regulations_made_in_exercise_of_the_power_conferred_by_paragraph_7_2_b_of_part_ii_of_schedule_8_to_the_1992_act
